This is a ScaleVideo plugin for the Video Disk Recorder (VDR).

Written by:                  Rolf Ahrenberg
                             < R o l f . A h r e n b e r g @ s c i . f i >

Project's homepage:          https://github.com/rofafor/vdr-plugin-scalevideo

Latest version available at: https://github.com/rofafor/vdr-plugin-scalevideo

